This project showcases an interactive Excel dashboard analyzing Adidas sales performance in the United States. The dashboard is designed to track key business metrics and provide actionable insights into sales trends.

🔑 Key Features

Sales analysis by region, state, and city

Product-wise and retailer-wise performance insights

KPIs including total revenue, profit, and units sold

Dynamic charts, slicers, and pivot tables for easy exploration

Simple, user-friendly design for quick decision-making

🛠️ Tools Used

Microsoft Excel – Dashboard creation, pivot tables, slicers, and charts

Data Cleaning & Preparation – Performed within Excel
